#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tick this box if you want &kget; to use default folders for your downloads."
msgstr ""
"Попуните ову кућицу ако желите да <application>К‑гет</application> преузима "
"у подразумеване фасцикле."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
